    },
    "schema:description": "Metadata harvested from SEANOE by the EarthCube GeoCodes catalog using Gleaner. Converted to CDIF Discovery profile: Property names prefixed with schema: namespace per CDIF convention; @context converted from @vocab style to explicit CDIF prefix declarations (schema, dcterms, dcat, prov); @type normalized to array format with schema: prefix; schema:dateModified set from schema:datePublished (original record lacked dateModified); schema:license wrapped in array; Distribution @type values normalized to arrays with schema: prefix; All nested @type values converted to arrays with schema: prefix. Round 2 CDIF fixes: subjectOf @type changed to [\"schema:Dataset\"] per CDIF CatalogRecord schema; subjectOf @id added (required by schema); schema:creator wrapped in @list to preserve author order per CDIF convention; Distribution encodingFormat wrapped in arrays; fileSize renamed to schema:contentSize; schema:spatialCoverage wrapped in array; @id set from schema:url; spatialCoverage strings converted to Place objects. Round 3 fixes: schema:keywords split from comma-separated string to array; variableMeasured propertyID values wrapped in arrays. Round 4 fixes: spatialCoverage geo unwrapped from array to single object.",
    "@id": "https://www.seanoe.org/data/00311/42182/#metadata"
  },
  "schema:dateModified": "2026-03-08",
